summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6206 for the improvement of West Kenyon Street from 45th Avenue Southwest to 46th Avenue Southwest; and a certain other street, by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 88410, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
